com.clover.sdk.v3.merchant

Class MerchantDevicesV2Connector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clover.sdk.v1.CallConnector
      • com.clover.sdk.v3.merchant.MerchantDevicesV2Connector

  • public class MerchantDevicesV2Connector
extends CallConnector
    Access information about devices associated with this merchant. This class contains convenience wrappers for accessing the data stored in the content provider at URI MerchantDevicesV2Contract.Device.CONTENT_URI.

    As the total number of devices for a merchant can be large, use MerchantDevicesV2Contract.Device to query for all (or a subset) of the merchant's devices.
